+  967|  1.11M|    std::string ConnectionTypeAsString() const { return ::ConnectionTypeAsString(m_conn_type); }
```

**`ForNode` — `net.cpp:4126-4131`**
```diff
-  4126|  1.08k|        if(pnode->GetId() == id) {
-    |  Branch (4126:12): [True: 0, False: 1.08k]
-  4127|      0|            found = pnode;
